## Security Reminders

- `.env`, `worker_key.json`, private keys → always in `.gitignore`, never committed
- `WORKER_PRIVATE_KEY` env injection is the production pattern (not file-based)
- RPC authentication via `X-API-Key` header when `AXIONAX_RPC_API_KEY` is set
- CORS restricted via `AXIONAX_RPC_CORS_ORIGINS` env
